    "candidate_observation_rule": "Write at least one candidate_own_view_refresh target for each materialized candidate row.",
    "pair_observation_rule": "Write one pair-level observation target for every unordered candidate pair. If a shared common view is not navigable/renderable, write a matched dual-standoff pair target with both candidate ids and the fallback reason.",
